name: Appartement Annakhil
description:
Located 2.6 km from Plage de Rabat and 1.2 km from The National Library of the Kingdom of Morocco in Rabat, Appartement Annakhil offers accommodation with a kitchen. Featuring a garden, the apartment is close to several noted attractions, around 2 km from Hassan Tower, 300 metres from National Office for Hydrocarbons and Mining and 500 metres from Moroccan Parliament. Free WiFi is available throughout the property and Plage de Salé Ville is 2.6 km away.

Opening onto a terrace with garden views, the spacious air-conditioned apartment consists of 1 bedroom. A flat-screen TV is provided. The accommodation is non-smoking.

Kasbah of the Udayas is 2.8 km from the apartment, while Bouregreg Marina is 3.9 km away. The nearest airport is Rabat-Salé Airport, 10 km from Appartement Annakhil.

name: Helnan Chellah Hotel
description:
Helnan Chellah Hotel is located in the centre of Rabat close to the attractions and shopping centres. Please note that access to our sauna is subject to a fee and is not free.

The Helnan Chellah has spacious rooms decorated with elegant furniture, and they include a minibar, air conditioning and a TV. The bathrooms are fitted with a bath and shower.
A buffet breakfast is prepared every morning at this hotel. Traditional meals are served in the restaurant, and you can enjoy refreshing drinks from the bar.

The airport is 12 km away and the nearest train station is Gare Rabat Ville, which is 1 km away. The Archaeology Museum is in front of the hotel, and the Royal Golf Dar Es Salam is 10 km away.
